258
00:09:33.874 --> 00:09:35.218
Right.

259
00:09:35.242 --> 00:09:36.753
You're kidding.

260
00:09:36.777 --> 00:09:38.245
Why?

261
00:09:40.180 --> 00:09:41.324
This is Joel Decker.

262
00:09:41.348 --> 00:09:42.726
Joel Decker
was part of your crew.

263
00:09:42.750 --> 00:09:44.560
